{"tid":953364,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知買咩車好, 熟車高手入","createTime":"2018-12-24T01:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T16:13:28.000Z","uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c196c0218f8ee4688390ab07ad92b6d2515b81c8","tid":953364,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"背景：美撚，有自己車房<br />\n自己揸緊2017 gti, 老婆揸緊2018 yaris ia<br />\n<br />\n想換架出黎靚靚仔仔既車，諗緊boxster/cayman呢類<br />\n或者f-type，唔熟車，有冇其他建議？<br />\n<br />\n但一定要自動波因為有時同我老婆交換車揸<br />\n有諗過miata, 但好似對比gti冇咩升級...<br />\nBrz/86果d唔會諗<br />\n<br />\n同埋工作有時需要，3幾年後可能有小朋友，而且我會成日去釣魚所以都要加多架suv（平平地toyota honda最入門級算）<br />\n<br />\n諗過model3但一街都係，而且長途好煩，玩過朋友果架一次roadtrip 冇feel唔想再揸<br />\n<br />\n所以有以下幾種諗法<br />\n<br />\n1）我換Macon搞掂 (對porsche有少少情意結，但同級bmw/audi都ok)<br />\n2) 我換miata+平suv/crossover<br />\n3）我換boxster，我老婆換suv (佢鍾意CH-R但我覺得太細，我支8尺魚杆都未必放得落）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點算好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287d166ffb586b9922558ca3fa60e13c16ff0f1e","tid":953364,"uid":11933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:37:10.000Z","msg":"Macao <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0473da72b79ae176c0d3f6f3af3b1ac8c23f5ce6","tid":953364,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"287d166ffb586b9922558ca3fa60e13c16ff0f1e","tid":953364,"uid":11933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:37:10.000Z","msg":"Macao <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"平+實用其實macan最岩我<br />\n但又想買架2門跑車...<br />\n<br />\nMacan點評價？同cayenne 比我鍾意macan外型多d"},{"pid":"e969038375d327ceec65d7b1c47799cd7b87f98c","tid":953364,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"新3系好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e5fe6fe608afc5dc3791964e62bad47f3e89be","tid":95336